PACKAGE   : sox
SUMMARY   : Buffer overflow vulnerability
DATE      : 2004-07-30 16:39:00
ID        : CLA-2004:855
RELEVANT
RELEASES  : 8, 9, 10

- -------------------------------------------------------------------------

DESCRIPTION
 SoX[1] is a general purpose sound file conversion tool.
 
 Ulf Hï¿½rnhammar found two buffer overflow vulnerabilities[2] in SoX.
 They occurred when the sox or play commands handled malicious .WAV
 files.


SOLUTION
 It is recommended that all SoX users upgrade their packages.
 
 
 REFERENCES
 1.http://sox.sourceforge.net/
 2.http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CAN-2004-0557


